comment: Lee (MEM) makes incidental contact with Gallinari (DEN) that does not affect his RSBQ.
Conley (MEM) makes incidental contact with Barton (DEN) that does not affect his RSBQ or shot attempt.
Lauvergne (DEN) makes contact with Gasol (MEM) that affects his FOM as he attempts to catch the pass.
Gasol (MEM) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact that does not affect Barton's (DEN) RSBQ on the baseline drive.
[Observable in enhanced video] Barton (DEN) establishes his right foot as his pivot and then picks it up.
Lauvergne (DEN) makes contact with Gasol's (MEM) arm as he attempts the driving layup.
Conley (MEM) maintains legal guarding position as he contests Gallinari's (DEN) jump shot attempt.
Mudiay (DEN) commits a take foul on Conley (MEM).
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that Mudiay (DEN) was behind the three point line and released the shot attempt prior to the clock expiring was confirmed.
